      "type": "text",
      "x": 900,
      "y": 162,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 250,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "\u2022 polls Worker: 10s live / 60s idle\n\n\u2022 normalizes ESPN in one seam\n  (src/lib/espn.ts)\n\n\u2022 computes standings, bracket,\n  scorers, upsets \u2014 client-side\n\n\u2022 renders terminal UI\n  (dark / light, responsive)",
      "originalText": "\u2022 polls Worker: 10s live / 60s idle\n\n\u2022 normalizes ESPN in one seam\n  (src/lib/espn.ts)\n\n\u2022 computes standings, bracket,\n  scorers, upsets \u2014 client-side\n\n\u2022 renders terminal UI\n  (dark / light, responsive)",
      "textAlign": "left",
